title: Ruined Tomb of Zallis
story: Zallis is long gone, but people are still reluctant to come close to the tomb. Recently it was squatted by a party of goblins. It is said that a legendary cape Bryxus is hidden here.

notes.text: A rear entrance into the tomb. A round wooden gate with three keyholes to the east.
A leather armor at the bottom of a pool.
A chest with a rapier and arrows in it.
A key among rubble on the ground.
A statue of a human, a key in its hands.
A key hidden in a crevice of the floor.
